snippet.title: Out of Ammo Full Release Trailer
snippet.description:
An intense virtual reality strategy game, Out of Ammo has you constructing defenses, calling in artillery, issuing orders, and even taking control of your soldiers directly in order to survive for as long as you can!

FOR THE HTC VIVE.

Available for purchase at: http://store.steampowered.com/app/451840

About RocketWerkz:

Founded in 2015 by Dean Hall, creator of DayZ, RocketWerkz is New Zealand's newest gaming studio. Located in Dunedin the studio is developing multiple titles for the PC and console. Out of Ammo is RocketWerkz first released game.

Trailer by Aaron Alexander
